":91153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a622494080a9d136f92103a63684fb56ac5db83c","tid":1098744,"uid":54627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"到而家淨係溫咗西周、春秋戰國、秦漢、安史至唐亡同宋朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"乙部呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實之前都熟民國之後啲史料，加上有讀世史，係唔知點解成日擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:11:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會溫埋列強的入侵同圖強運動呀?"},{"pid":"7b26efcbb11415714bbe3363afd34b20a1eb99e5","tid":1098744,"uid":91153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5a0f3c26c01b0bfe41f0a60f73c82e176bbe554","tid":1098744,"uid":135291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"今年有咩重點要温<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"你打算溫咩TOPIC??"},{"pid":"cb8ba5298fda6ee18991ed5a2964f23ec15929e4","tid":1098744,"uid":91153,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2230f3d81d7f190ac2cea1b40b07c55f1b0c4440","tid":1098744,"uid":202694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:30:05.000Z","msg":"有冇宗教史tips<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"宗教史方面<br />\n天主基督一定會嫁啦<br />\n同學要知道 利瑪竇點解調和中西文化 將天文教打入中國市場(以學輔教 滇繹教義 直叩朝廷)<br />\n貢獻 同之後點解會衍生到禮儀之爭<br />\n今年重點應該係禁教 要知南京教案 康熙曆獄 禮儀之爭既因由<br />\n馬禮遜都係點解決佢既困難 最重要係識比較<br />\n<br />\n道教方面 上年問左滅佛同埋東漢道教既緣起<br />\n今年可能會出東漢同魏晉南北朝道教既對比"},{"pid":"ffc52125f5c8b8b4ba80374f209991ed390aba99","tid":1098744,"uid":135291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi